674
00:45:25,600 --> 00:45:26,220
Zi.

675
00:45:41,270 --> 00:45:42,080
Xing.

676
00:45:42,920 --> 00:45:44,250
Kita fikirkan cara lain.

677
00:45:44,480 --> 00:45:45,660
Awak tak boleh berlatih.

678
00:45:46,580 --> 00:45:47,370
Tapi...

679
